General.Name: Minesto AB
General.GicIndustry: Independent Power and Renewable Electricity Producers
General.Description: Minesto AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, operates as a marine energy developer in Sweden, Wales, the Faroe Islands, Northern Ireland, and Taiwan. Its Deep Green technology produces electricity from tidal streams and ocean currents through a turbine. Minesto AB (publ) was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Vastra Frolunda, Sweden.
